name: Corn
description: In a land far away sunlight shines on a corn field that slowly grows among the sounds of crows hovering above and a mountain breeze that whispers past its tall stalks reaching for the sky. Until the harvest there are no people in this moment of time and place except me and the camera as a witness on my daily walks capturing the beauty in nature and share it with you here and now. 3965 × 3965 pixels 300dpi digital photograph.
